org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity This package contains classes which define the various BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity.support This package contains classes which support various BPEL activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.convert.visitors This package contains visitors which are used to convert from one version of BPEL to another. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.ext This package contains the classes for reading and writing extension elements for BPEL.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefReader interface for reading in BPEL xml and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers This package provides the impl classes for the IAeBpelWriter interface.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefWriter interface for serializing specific AeBaseDef object subclasses and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation This package contains classes which support BPEL validation.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity This package contains implementation classes for activity validation models. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.process   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors Classes implementing the Visitor pattern used to perform various functions on the activity definitions.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.preprocess.strategies.wsio Visitors and supporting classes for determining the proper strategy for wsio activities and their message data production or consumption. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity This package contains classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy Process deployment.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.validate Root package for the Active Endpoints BPEL Deployment Validation code.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview This package contains all the code and presentation beans for driving the web app Process Details view ui.
